# HEXROLL 3 CHANGELOG

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
## [0.7.3 build-2606250030] - 2026-06-25

### Fixed
- Fixed OS window scaling affecting UI and rendering buffer sizes
- Fixed MacOS issues with optimized-for-size config


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
## [0.7.2 build-2606191648] - 2026-06-24

### Changed
- Changed opacity for partially revealed tiles

### Fixed
- Fixed a crash when VTT players explore a battlemap
- Fixed a bug when revealing battlemaps to players
- Fixed a few 5E modifier calculation issues


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
## [0.7.1 build-2606191648] - 2026-06-20

### Added
- Solo sandbox generation and play mode
- Hybrid terrain generator / editor
- New underground / overland layering system
- F1 toggle for a keyboard shortcuts overlay (still work-in-progress)

### Changed
- Searching is now enabled in split view
- Added content cache to reduce rendering time

### Fixed
- Fixed a crash when re-rolling a dungeon corridor
- Fixed sigils not showing correctly for keys
- Realms and regions are now shown on the map when selected
- Ocean hexes instantiating & revealing works correctly now
- Fixed another case of duplicate dice frame buffers
- A few more minor tweaks and fixes


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
## [-.-.- build-2605240910] - 2026-05-24

### Added
- Standalone-mode VTT is now supported
- 5E is now available for standalone sandboxes
- Map editor now has additional feature tools and will pre-populate hexes
- Rollback any sandbox change using ctrl-z / cmd-z (one-way-only) 
- Renaming NPCs is now supported

### Changed
- Added a scrollbar to the content page

### Fixed
- Possibly fixed a render-buffer glitch when rolling dice
- Fixed a crash when re-rolling ocean hexes
- Fixed spoilers in standalone-mode
- Fixed "losing" the map due to camera moving out-of-bounds
- Other minor fixes and UX improvements


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
## [-.-.- build-2604231315] - 2026-04-25

### Added
- Standalone mode - generate and use OSR sandboxes locally
- Hex map editor - draw your hex map using basic map editing tools
- Non-linear generation - generate things in any order

### Changed
- Rolling D100 using the '0' key will now roll a D10 as well

### Fixed
- Fixed a crash when minimizing hexroll in Windows
- Fixed some tile-art glitches
